class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tayeb2\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f489747562a9f80f080a58a77984e5fc?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f489747562a9f80f080a58a77984e5fc?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tayeb2\" class=\"reviewer-name\">tayeb2</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 28, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">can you please stop the message alert. by the way ..I really like Orbit Fox .. 5 stars for u.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Some starting difficulties – buth then …</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/renedeutscher\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/dd5b634995efcd1cb4c489d3919ea19d?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/dd5b634995efcd1cb4c489d3919ea19d?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/renedeutscher\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Ren? Deutscher <small>(renedeutscher)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 27, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I had an bad error which made my website unusable.\nWith the help of support we fixed the problem!\n\nMANY THANKS!\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Orbit Fox by Themelsle</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/steshie1991\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1fa1d56c5be963226e02909f640b8d17?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1fa1d56c5be963226e02909f640b8d17?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/steshie1991\" class=\"reviewer-name\">steshie1991</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 25, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Wonderful plugin. I could not wish for any other! :) :)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Good</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/chua94\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ea0aec1a8669debd52f15d443a732f06?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ea0aec1a8669debd52f15d443a732f06?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/chua94\" class=\"reviewer-name\">chua94</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 14, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Great! Easy to use</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Muito bom</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/nelsoncatato\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/628863c6c616716b2906aa5915ea6856?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/628863c6c616716b2906aa5915ea6856?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/nelsoncatato\" class=\"reviewer-name\">nelsoncatato</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 25, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">vale 5 estrelas </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">So far... so GREAT!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/coachericka\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/cab7974b070508968ce13d31012a3182?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/cab7974b070508968ce13d31012a3182?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/coachericka\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Ericka <small>(coachericka)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 23, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Orbit Fox has performed perfectly in every way I\'ve needed it to. Thank you!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Very helpful plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tomislavco\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1dd72aea9f9468b54c3b26b805408abb?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1dd72aea9f9468b54c3b26b805408abb?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tomislavco\" class=\"reviewer-name\">tomislavco</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 19, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Thank you very much for a such great plugin!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Easy to Use</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/abdulmuhajir\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8651b7223c6ee9db3402d504d562ab5d?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8651b7223c6ee9db3402d504d562ab5d?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/abdulmuhajir\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Abdul Muhajir <small>(abdulmuhajir)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 8, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Simple plugin and very easy to use.</div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:159:\"This swiss-knife plugin comes with a quality template library, menu/sharing icons, Gutenberg blocks and newly added Elementor/BeaverBuilder page build &hellip;\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:62:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/themeisle-companion.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:5:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:72:\"https://ps.w.org/themeisle-companion/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=2237652\";s:7:\"caption\";s:27:\"The OrbitFox Dashboard Page\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:72:\"https://ps.w.org/themeisle-companion/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=2237652\";s:7:\"caption\";s:27:\"The Template Directory Page\";}i:3;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:72:\"https://ps.w.org/themeisle-companion/assets/screenshot-3.png?rev=2237652\";s:7:\"caption\";s:17:\"Menu Icons Module\";}i:4;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:72:\"https://ps.w.org/themeisle-companion/assets/screenshot-4.png?rev=2237652\";s:7:\"caption\";s:31:\"Page Builder Widgets and Addons\";}i:5;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:72:\"https://ps.w.org/themeisle-companion/assets/screenshot-5.png?rev=2237652\";s:7:\"caption\";s:21:\"Social Sharing Module\";}}s:8:\"versions\";a:81:{s:5:\"1.0.0\";s:68:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/themeisle-companion.1.0.0.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.1\";s:68:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/themeisle-companion.1.0.1.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.2\";s:68:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/themeisle-companion.1.0.2.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.3\";s:6