</div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/maxdosh\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8534500523022093077903d7d6c5ba0c?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8534500523022093077903d7d6c5ba0c?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/maxdosh\" class=\"reviewer-name\">maxdosh</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 14, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I like the plugin. It gets the job done in a simple way.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Cool</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"4 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"4\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mbican\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f63d407b2a1fa13605b36ec171e18cbc?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f63d407b2a1fa13605b36ec171e18cbc?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mbican\" class=\"reviewer-name\">mbican</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 9, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Easy to use, lite vesion is enough for me</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Just What I Was Looking For</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/moneta48\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/161785d067390c39370e985168a695ba?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/161785d067390c39370e985168a695ba?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/moneta48\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Moneta48</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 21, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Adds more information for the products on my page.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">reviews</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/sweetsavorymeals\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/fc6304df9010803f19a562b51a32c81d?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/fc6304df9010803f19a562b51a32c81d?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/sweetsavorymeals\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Catalina Castravet <small>(sweetsavorymeals)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">January 27, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">good</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">very goog</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/luketapis\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/77d64eb78c3b403cc21f64cb866e4c5e?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/77d64eb78c3b403cc21f64cb866e4c5e?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/luketapis\" class=\"reviewer-name\">luketapis</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">January 5, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I really like it</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great plugin!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/merval\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d1bb521b03f026ffd34e704787e2a24f?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d1bb521b03f026ffd34e704787e2a24f?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/merval\" class=\"reviewer-name\">merval</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">October 19, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">This plugin is really straight forward to use and provides a great way to give a product a review. There are others do similar stuff, but this one is by far the easiest to use and has the best output.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Flabbergasting good!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/bussies\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/4a5a8836c3dc40248de0b8cdbd545080?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/4a5a8836c3dc40248de0b8cdbd545080?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/bussies\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Stijn Debusschere <small>(bussies)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">September 22, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Great!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">works as described!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/deranged_dev\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/beb9dbeadbcc6238684d3fefc0a8b7ea?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/beb9dbeadbcc6238684d3fefc0a8b7ea?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/deranged_dev\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Deranged_Dev</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">October 6, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">pretty to look at, a lot of customization features. Doesn\'t ask to purchase premium all the time. Can recommend.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">WP Product Review</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/trekoutcast\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/bc746f02c052704e8a4ae17d9eae0284?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/bc746f02c052704e8a4ae17d9eae0284?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/trekoutcast\" class=\"reviewer-name\">trekoutcast</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">August 24, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Simple and Great!</div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:128:\"Easily turn your basic posts into in-depth reviews with ratings, pros and cons, affiliate links, rich snippets and user reviews.\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:60:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/wp-product-review.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:7:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:69:\"https://ps.w.org/wp-product-review/trunk/screenshot-1.png?rev=2249292\";s:7:\"caption\";s:72:\"Screenshot 1 Wrap-up review widget that is added at the end of the posts\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:69:\"https://ps.w.org/wp-product-review/trunk/screenshot-2.png?rev=2249292\";s:7:\"caption\";s:62:\"Screenshot 2 Review comment on a scale of 5 with slider rating\";}i:3;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:69:\"https://ps.w.org/wp-product-review/trunk/screenshot-3.png?rev=2249292\";s:7:\"caption\";s:63:\"Screenshot 3 Review comment on a scale of 10 with slider rating\";}i:4;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:69:\"https://ps.w.org/wp-product-review/trunk/screenshot-4.png?rev=2249292\";s:7:\"caption\";s:44:\"Screenshot 4 Review comment with star rating\";}i:5;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:69:\"https://ps.w.org/wp-product-review/trunk/screenshot-5.png?rev=2249292\";s:7:\"caption\";s:42:\"Screenshot 5 Settings configuration screen\";}i:6;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:69:\"https://ps.w.org/wp-product-review/trunk/screenshot-6.png?rev=2249292\";s:7:\"caption\";s:46:\"Screenshot 6 Rich Snippets displayed in Google\";}i:7;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:69:\"https://ps.w.org/wp-product-review/trunk/screenshot-7.png?rev=2249292\";s:7:\"caption\";s:43:\"Screenshot 7 How ratings appear as comments\";}}s:8:\"versions\";a:56:{s:3:\"1.1\";s:64:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/wp-product-review.1.1.zip\";s:5:\"2.2.4\";s:66:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/wp-product-review.2.2.4.zip\";s:5:\"2.2.7\";s:66:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/wp-product-review.2.2.7.zip\";s:5:\"2.4.7\";s:66:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/wp-product-review.2.4.7.zip\";s:5:\"2.6.9\";s:66:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/wp-product-review.2.6.9.zip\";s:5:\"2.7.2\";s:66:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/wp-product-review.2.7.2.zip\";s:5:\"2.8.0\";s:66:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/wp-product-review.2.8.0.zip\";s:5:\"2.8.1\";s:66:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/wp-product-review.2.8.1.zip\";s:5:\"2.8.7\";s:66:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/wp-product-review.2.8.7.zip\";s:5:\"2.9.0\";s:66:\"https://downloads.wordp