o install!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/letstalkfurbabiesnow\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/223e8031c46914ef8dd98ad6a8af255c?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/223e8031c46914ef8dd98ad6a8af255c?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/letstalkfurbabiesnow\" class=\"reviewer-name\">letstalkfurbabiesnow</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 29, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">This plug in was so easy to use, and it works great. I have never Blogged or created a Site before, if I can use this so can you. </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Excellent plug in</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/thewijk\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/74074e070d8c97f3f9e36e57844b2b6a?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/74074e070d8c97f3f9e36e57844b2b6a?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/thewijk\" class=\"reviewer-name\">thewijk</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 29, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Easy to use and works fine</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">EXCELENTE</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/claudisom\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8cc13e1a49844481c32a9733b872058e?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8cc13e1a49844481c32a9733b872058e?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/claudisom\" class=\"reviewer-name\">claudisom</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 29, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">EXCELENTE</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Excelente plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/alfsotomayorg\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/13c65fe53a798a47ad8a154ece29bb21?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/13c65fe53a798a47ad8a154ece29bb21?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/alfsotomayorg\" class=\"reviewer-name\">alfsotomayorg</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 29, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">sin tanto manejo de códigos como otros, este sólo es arrastrar cajas y es muy sencillo de programar su funcionalidad</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Thank you for the great Plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/lemanja\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/fa8ad0b9d463c0f4a139870b861417f6?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/fa8ad0b9d463c0f4a139870b861417f6?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/lemanja\" class=\"reviewer-name\">lemanja</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 29, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I absolutely love this Plugin. Excellent product.</div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:145:\"The best WordPress contact form plugin. Drag &amp; Drop online form builder that helps you create beautiful contact forms with just a few clicks.\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:63:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/wpforms-lite.1.5.9.5.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:6:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:65:\"https://ps.w.org/wpforms-lite/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=1815766\";s:7:\"caption\";s:43:\"WPForms Drag &amp; Drop Online Form Builder\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:65:\"https://ps.w.org/wpforms-lite/assets/screenshot-2.gif?rev=1815770\";s:7:\"caption\";s:16:\"Adding New Field\";}i:3;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:65:\"https://ps.w.org/wpforms-lite/assets/screenshot-3.png?rev=1815766\";s:7:\"caption\";s:12:\"Form Preview\";}i:4;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:65:\"https://ps.w.org/wpforms-lite/assets/screenshot-4.png?rev=1815766\";s:7:\"caption\";s:13:\"Form Settings\";}i:5;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:65:\"https://ps.w.org/wpforms-lite/assets/screenshot-5.gif?rev=2037397\";s:7:\"caption\";s:26:\"Conversational Forms addon\";}i:6;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:65:\"https://ps.w.org/wpforms-lite/assets/screenshot-6.png?rev=2037397\";s:7:\"caption\";s:16:\"Form Pages addon\";}}s:8:\"versions\";a:87:{s:5:\"1.1.4\";s:61:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/wpforms-lite.1.1.4.zip\";s:7:\"1.1.4.2\";s:63:\"https://d